events.title: Cindy Hudspeth, who Felicia Waller is based on, is killed

movie.title: The Hillside Strangler
movie.plot: Kenneth Bianchi is a security guard whose attempts to become a police officer are repeatedly thwarted. He moves to California to live with his cousin Angelo and dates a string of women, becoming increasingly preoccupied with sex. Eventually the cousins decide to start an escort agency. After violently killing a prostitute they thought had betrayed them, Kenneth and Angelo begin committing a series of crimes that become a media sensation.

events.title: Tonya Harding lands a triple axle at the nationals

movie.title: I, Tonya
movie.plot: Competitive ice skater Tonya Harding rises amongst the ranks at the U. S. Figure Skating Championships, but her future in the sport is thrown into doubt when her ex-husband intervenes.

events.title: Joel and Clementine realise they have erased each other from their memories

movie.title: Eternal Sunshine of the Spotless Mind
movie.plot: Joel Barish, heartbroken that his girlfriend underwent a procedure to erase him from her memory, decides to do the same. However, as he watches his memories of her fade away, he realises that he still loves her, and may be too late to correct his mistake.
